Kara ha naɨngwowi Bɨiyan Inkam Komii Jisɨs Krais siir naɨngwombumbuwa, saeya kɨmakar dwokrɨpkai. Ta yaiya saeya kaimwo ywokiya. Ɨriig.
Tɨ nomiiyauɨm kɨma bɨiya Adi Komii siya nɨmbina ɨiya kɨma naɨngwo tɨbmiiya mɨ saiiram tɨ swokɨ aɨngwowoknaki bɨiya kɨma panɨɨn panɨɨn inkam nwokɨm, ɨiya Adi Komii siya kɨmiir nɨmbina. Mɨ nu tɨran iikamɨm nɨnoknɨnkɨn komii Komiigakɨm mɨ kɨrɨe komii komiigak nwokɨm, yɨm ɨuarɨg bɨ nwokɨm. Nɨɨngakɨ, nɨɨngakɨɨnga.
Mɨ inkamɨn sasaeya nɨnkɨniyɨn, yɨo inɨg karamaekɨn mɨ ko numɨr nakiyɨn, yɨo ɨriipɨ hɨriinan, inɨg karamaekɨn. Sasae ɨmiirɨn Adi Komii krɨmiir Wanɨn siyar dirɨraerarki mɨ sɨma pa nɨmbiyami mɨ inɨgakɨn pɨ Adi Komii siyar nwowi.
Kara ta yaiya kɨmiir kiyopsɨbgi haigɨnɨuam bɨ wɨnkika. Nɨɨngaka. Kɨma ɨni kariir yɨnisɨsɨmnan ywowɨm mɨ kariir kwoɨnɨn ɨni kɨmiiramar naɨngwo ɨrkakɨn mɨ ta yokwowa kara wɨnkiya kara kɨmiirsi kauɨdidgikɨn.
